Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.22,0:22:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}The rudder named Kókkalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.28,0:22:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}And the freedom available from the rudder.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.43,0:22:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}Though we have found more possibilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.39,0:22:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}the mud whale lost its destination
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}and started to wander.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}The yoke of the truth of our short-lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.65,0:22:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}was pressing me...
